# HospitalManagement-Using-JDBC



HOSPITAL MANAGEMENT SYSTEM


 

Step 1. The program should display the menu as follows
1 : Admin
2 : Opstaff
3: Exit
Admin:
Step 2. If 1 is pressed, get the admin login details and validate. On valid login, show  the below menu.

1 : Emergency
2 : Outpatient(OP)
3 : Logout

Step 3. If 1 is pressed, get the emergency details, show the below menu.
1)Add(doctor) // (Fields:id,name,department,start time,end time,fee)
2)Delete(doctor) // (Fields:id)
3)Update(doctor) // (Fields:id,start time,end time,fee)
4)Display // (Field:id,name,department,start time,end time,fee)
5)Exit  // (Should display menu on step 2)
	3.1 Add doctor details into table.
	3.2 Remove the details of  doctor with given id.
	3.3 Update field time and fee with given id.
	3.4 display all details of the doctor.
	3.5 go back to previous menu .
Step 4. If 2 press get OP details and show the menu given below
1)Add(doctor) // (Fields:id,name,department,start time,end time,fee)
2)Delete(doctor) // (Fields:id)
3)Update(doctor) // (Fields:id,start time,end time,fee)
4)Display // (Field:id,name,department,start time,end time,fee)
5)Exit  // (Should display menu on step 2)
	4.1 Add doctor details into table.
	4.2 Remove the details of  doctor with given id.
	4.3 Update field time and fee with given id.
	4.4 display all details of the doctor.
	4.5 go back to previous menu .
Step 5. Logout Should display the menu on Step 1. Note: Until logout, the menu on step 2 should be repeated.
OP Staff
Step 6.  If 2 is pressed, get the opstaff login details and validate. On valid login, show  the below menu.

1 : Emergency
2 : Outpatient(OP)
3 : Logout

Step 7. If 1 is pressed, get the emergency details, show the below menu.
1 :Available doctor// (Field:id,name,age,gender,address)
2 : Add Patient // (Field:id,name,age,gender,address)
3 : Exit
  7.1  Display the available doctors details
  7.2  Add patient details and print the bill also.
  7.3 go back to previous section(step 6)
Step 8. If 2 is pressed,get the OP details,show the below menu. 
1 :Available doctor// (Field:id,name,age,gender,address)
2 : Add Patient // (Field:id,name,age,gender,address)
3 : Exit
    8.1  Display the available doctors details
    8.2  Add patient details and print the bill also.
8.2.1 Ask department of doctor,then print available doctor name , time and fee.
8.2.2 Ask which doctor you want.
8.2.3 print patient id ,name,doctor name,fee; including fee of opticket also.
 8.3 go back to previous section(step 6)

Instruction:
1.	Predefined list of Admin and OP staff( at least 2 users in Admin and 2 in OPstaff) with min field(username,password).
2.	Accessing the details using database is preffered .
3.	The given fields on the questions are the mandatory fields. You are allowed to add additional tables or fields based on your design to meet the above said functionality.

Output
1 : Admin
2 : Opstaff
3 : Exit
